182
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:56,160
and I'll rip your tongue out.

183
00:11:56,160 --> 00:11:57,350
Birds of a feather

184
00:11:57,670 --> 00:11:58,840
flock together.

185
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:00,870
