188
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,280
Isn't a tiger fierce?

189
00:12:04,510 --> 00:12:06,270
Yet it's still the king of beasts.

190
00:12:06,270 --> 00:12:07,800
She's no queen of anything.

191
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,720
Huo Du escaped.

192
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:10,120
And I was going after him.

193
00:12:10,130 --> 00:12:12,170
I was just cleaning up her mess.

194
00:12:12,420 --> 00:12:14,390
She said
I didn't respect her as my sister,

195
00:12:14,390 --> 00:12:16,120
and she used Dad to pressure me.

196
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,600
I think she doesn't treat us

197
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,750
like family.

198
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:20,080
Such an ingrate.

199
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:22,460
