233
00:14:56,860 --> 00:14:57,650
You

234
00:14:59,000 --> 00:14:59,960
are

235
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:02,040
a good person.

236
00:15:35,030 --> 00:15:35,990
Captain.

237
00:15:38,630 --> 00:15:39,270
Captain.

238
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:40,270
Captain,

239
00:15:40,270 --> 00:15:41,030
